from 1914 to 1945

44
00:05:41,299 --> 00:05:45,298
more than 100 million people will die

45
00:05:45,299 --> 00:05:48,967
in the bloodiest conflict
the world has ever seen.

46
00:05:50,634 --> 00:05:52,298
But it all began

47
00:05:52,299 --> 00:05:55,008
in the slums of Vienna.

48
00:05:55,009 --> 00:05:57,729
